name: Self Portrait for 3D scan, light bulb and glitch
description:
Francesca Fini, 2021
3D Scanner, Meshlab, Blender, Photoshop

3D photography is a dynamic, empirical, unpredictable experience. A dance with light that relies on the imperfect intelligence of the device, which interprets, senses, reconstructs and puts together our fragmentary image based on algorithms and models. In this project I tried my best to deeply stress the system, opening the way to the beauty of error and glitch.
